title: Зірконавти
overview: "Zirkonavty" is a new explosive comedy series on TET. Finally a team of Ukrainian cosmonauts will fly into space! A secret laboratory accidentally made an incredible discovery – our scientists have invented a super fuel in the form of a regular pill.Now, with almost unlimited energy resources at their disposal, researchers decide to organize the First Ukrainian space mission. Time is short, the crew is chosen in a hurry, and the purpose of the mission and generally forget to determine. What will happen? Follow the incredible adventures of our star scouts on TET or online. Find out how the First Ukrainian mission in space ends!
